        {
            "title": "納芯微超額認購逾24倍　卓越睿新超額認購逾4812倍",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">2隻下周一主板上市的新股公布招股結果，納芯微(02676)超額認購24.33倍，卓越睿新(02687)超購4812.4倍。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：納芯微官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251022_FI_source-web_688052-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：納芯微官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251022_FI_source-web_688052-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：納芯微官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">納芯微每手100股，一手中籤率為4.32%，國際發售部分超額認購近2倍。股份以招股價範圍上限116元定價，集資淨額約21億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">卓越睿新公開發售部分超額認購逾4812.4倍，每手100股，一手中籤率為1%，國際發售部分超額認購1.33倍。股份以67.5元定價，接近招股價62.26元至76.1元下限，集資淨額約3.9億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">納芯微(02676)周五暗盤收跌約9%， 上海卓越睿新數碼科技(02687)則升約三成。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15484306-%e7%b4%8d%e8%8a%af%e5%be%ae%e8%b6%85%e9%a1%8d%e8%aa%8d%e8%b3%bc%e9%80%be24%e5%80%8d%e3%80%80%e5%8d%93%e8%b6%8a%e7%9d%bf%e6%96%b0%e8%b6%85%e9%a1%8d%e8%aa%8d%e8%b3%bc%e9%80%be4812%e5%80%8d-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/Able-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-06 12:50:27",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美債息升  10 年期國債息率本周累升逾12基點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國國債息率升，10年期國債息率曾升3.9基點，歐債國債息率也向上。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"美國國債。\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/01/20240103_BLOG_-5.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"美國國債。\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/01/20240103_BLOG_-5.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">美國國債。</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">紐約尾市，美國10年期國債收益率漲3.69個基點，報4.1351厘，曾升3.9基點，至4.148厘，本周累計上漲12.18個基點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">兩年期美債收益率漲3.77個基點，報3.5603%，本周累漲7.10個基點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">據芝加哥商品交易所(CME)的FedWatch工具顯示，交易員預計聯儲局下周議息後減息的可能性高達87%，遠高於數周前的預測。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">歐市尾市，德國10年期國債收益率漲2.8個基點，報2.798厘，本周累計上漲11.0個基點。兩年期德債收益率漲2.1個基點，報2.095厘，本周累漲6.6個基點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">本周，英國10年期國債收益率累計上漲3.6個基點，周五（12月5日）歐市尾盤報4.476厘。兩年期英債收益率累漲3.6個基點，報3.381厘。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15485017-%e7%be%8e%e5%82%b5%e6%81%af%e5%8d%87-10-%e5%b9%b4%e6%9c%9f%e5%9c%8b%e5%82%b5%e6%81%af%e7%8e%87%e6%9c%ac%e5%91%a8%e7%b4%af%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be12%e5%9f%ba%e9%bb%9e",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20190902_FI_US-TREASURY-BONDS_US-BOND_FB-1-2-1-1-1-1_source-web_-1-2-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-06 12:35:27",
